  _eventName: 'Hot days: A record year for extreme temperatures'
  _date: September 21, 2024
  _subheading: "This summer will be remembered as one of the hottest in decades.
    The country recorded several hot days, with temperatures regularly exceeding
    35\xB0C in many regions. This series of heat waves highlights the effects of
    global warming and raises growing concerns about the consequences for health,
    the environment and infrastructure."
